Dialogue: 5,0:01:59.37,0:02:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The mushi are restless here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.21,0:02:37.26,Mushisode Title,,0,0,0,eptitle,{\fad(2000,0)\an9\bord0\blur0.6\p1\c&H5FAAA1&\pos(1282,68)\fscx600\fscy90}m 0 0 l 100 0 100 100 0 100
Dialogue: 2,0:02:31.21,0:02:37.26,Mushisode Title,,0,0,0,eptitle,{\an6\fad(2000,0)\blur0.6\pos(1100,110)}The Cushion of Grass
Dialogue: 5,0:02:45.68,0:02:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What are you?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:55.85,0:02:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Are you planning on eating me?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:03.75,0:03:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Are you afraid of me?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:11.35,0:03:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nah, you're just watching me...
Dialogue: 5,0:03:20.97,0:03:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and trying to figure out what I am.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:55.17,0:03:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, looks like you're human after all.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:00.05,0:04:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Green eyes...
Dialogue: 5,0:04:02.80,0:04:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,and white hair.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:06.15,0:04:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard of you.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:08.95,0:04:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,"There is a unnatural child who attracts mushi and causes disasters wherever he goes."
Dialogue: 5,0:04:16.32,0:04:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I've also heard that plenty of mushi-shi have taken you in.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:19.38,0:04:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Did another one throw you out or something?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:24.06,0:04:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Why stick around and let mushi get lured in?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:27.53,0:04:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You can prevent disasters from happening as long as you keep moving, you know.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:33.55,0:04:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I do it to earn my keep.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:36.00,0:04:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I attract mushi, and the mushi-shi resolves whatever problems arise.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:40.78,0:04:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just that every now and then, \Nthings get out of hand.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:45.64,0:04:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are the kind of people \Nwho usually take you in, huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:53.09,0:04:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Suguro.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:54.87,0:04:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a mushi-shi who lives in these mountains.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:58.94,0:04:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 5,0:05:03.49,0:05:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:04.90,0:05:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,A Tokoyami, or "Eternal Darkness" mushi, \Nis trapped here.{Tokoyami: Eternal darkness}
Dialogue: 5,0:05:09.90,0:05:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You were probably swallowed by one in the past.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:13.91,0:05:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That explains your peculiar constitution as well.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:17.59,0:05:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,A Tokoyami?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:19.44,0:05:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,None of the other mushi-shi told you{ about it}?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:21.90,0:05:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a mushi as pitch-black as pure darkness.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:24.98,0:05:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Your memories before a certain point \Nhave disappeared too, right?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:28.40,0:05:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It also eats memories.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:31.11,0:05:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So if you take it out,
Dialogue: 5,0:05:33.32,0:05:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll become normal again, right?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:36.33,0:05:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just a mushi trapped in your body.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:39.31,0:05:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Tokoyami don't attract other mushi.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:43.55,0:05:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to say, but that's all you.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:47.37,0:05:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,People like you crop up every so often,
Dialogue: 5,0:05:50.50,0:05:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,but no one's ever found a way to treat that condition.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:54.94,0:05:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, all you can do is accept it.{'that reality', but reuse of 'that'}
Dialogue: 5,0:06:03.35,0:06:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,In any case, I scattered the mushi that were surrounding you.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:06.23,0:06:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It should hold for a few days.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:08.69,0:06:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Before you go, you should regain your strength \Nso you don't collapse again.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:16.99,0:06:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there a River of Light here?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:21.21,0:06:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, there is.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:24.49,0:06:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Then... that must have been the mountain lord.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:32.34,0:06:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to keep an eye on me, you know.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:35.31,0:06:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like I'm going to settle down here.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:55.41,0:06:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,"Ginko," was it?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:57.81,0:06:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're well enough to walk, come with me.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:16.12,0:07:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Did they teach you anything about basic herbs, at least?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:20.00,0:07:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,A bit.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:22.05,0:07:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The herbs on this mountain are especially potent.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:24.94,0:07:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Take some with you.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:28.13,0:07:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Learn how to make mushi-repellent cigarettes yourself, too.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:31.36,0:07:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It won't just lessen the effect you have on your surroundings.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:35.95,0:07:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll also protect you from \Nany mushi-related diseases.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:59.13,0:08:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,A beautiful place, isn't it?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:04.13,0:08:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't let you stay for long,
Dialogue: 5,0:08:06.31,0:08:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,but if you stop by \Nonce in a while just to say hello,
Dialogue: 5,0:08:08.32,0:08:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure the mountain lord won't mind too much.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:22.58,0:08:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Suguro.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:24.62,0:08:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:26.04,0:08:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That boy's not from around here, is he?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:28.78,0:08:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just looking after him for a little while.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:33.41,0:08:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You could say he's my apprentice.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:35.88,0:08:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, where are your manners?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:38.98,0:08:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:41.13,0:08:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:42.32,0:08:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, good luck to you, kiddo.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:45.00,0:08:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,So, how are things looking?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:46.69,0:08:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Do we have a new mountain lord yet?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:49.12,0:08:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not yet.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:51.80,0:08:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't a new one have been born by now?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:54.44,0:08:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 5,0:08:56.00,0:08:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Come now, there's no reason to be so concerned.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:59.67,0:09:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Worrying won't make a difference.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:01.60,0:09:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The flowers will bloom \Nand bear fruit like they do every year.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:05.23,0:09:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That's simply the natural order of things.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:16.37,0:09:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What was all that talk about a new mountain lord?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:24.10,0:09:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Even mountain lords are mortal.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:27.16,0:09:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The one here is nearing the end of its life.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:32.45,0:09:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But for some reason, we still \Nhaven't seen any sign of its successor.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:38.09,0:09:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,If there's no lord when this one dies, these mountains will decline.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:42.47,0:09:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what has everyone so worried.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:46.85,0:09:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,If one never showed up, what would that mean?{reworded this slightly to make it clearer that no new lord is a symptom more than the direct cause of the world declining}
Dialogue: 5,0:09:51.74,0:09:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,In time, the whole world would fall apart.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:55.86,0:09:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like I mentioned.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:57.50,0:10:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The lack of a mountain lord would be like flowers not blooming in the springtime.{technically this "flowers" should be possessive (with an apostrophe: flowers'), but that would probably distract people more than being technically incorrect, so it's left out. http://www.quickanddirtytips.com/education/grammar/do-i-hate-your-singing-or-you-singing}
Dialogue: 5,0:10:03.70,0:10:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,They are embodiments of the natural order of life.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:08.28,0:10:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Mountain lords signify the bond between \Nthe mountains and the natural order itself.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:31.50,0:10:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:33.14,0:10:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The mountain lord isn't watching me anymore.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:46.38,0:10:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:50.99,0:10:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I think the mountain lord has passed away.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:55.77,0:10:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go take a look around.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:57.30,0:10:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You stay here.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:01.41,0:11:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Did this happen because of me{I showed up}?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:04.80,0:11:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't I tell you it was on its last legs?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:07.84,0:11:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,However, its successor still hasn't appeared.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:11.55,0:11:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,There's unrest in the mountains.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:13.32,0:11:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You should stay here.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:16.22,0:11:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:39.11,0:11:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:43.39,0:11:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be...
Dialogue: 5,0:12:06.49,0:12:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Does this egg... belong to the mountain lord?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:13.25,0:12:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:18.68,0:12:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a successor after all.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:36.48,0:12:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All the mountain lord's power lies inside this little egg.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:44.86,0:12:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It{ is a being that}'s the complete opposite of me.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:49.82,0:12:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's... the chosen one.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:01.74,0:13:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I...
Dialogue: 5,0:13:05.75,0:13:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I were to act right now, \Ncould I make its power mine?{pls}
Dialogue: 5,0:13:17.62,0:13:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't be foolish.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:19.93,0:13:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What the hell are you thinking?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:43.61,0:13:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What the...
Dialogue: 5,0:13:46.56,0:13:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:01.63,0:14:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What do I do?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:03.38,0:14:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I...
Dialogue: 5,0:14:06.34,0:14:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Suguro.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:08.45,0:14:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Suguro!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:20.47,0:14:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Its light is getting fainter.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:25.60,0:14:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I don't do something quick...
Dialogue: 5,0:14:33.93,0:14:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Mountain Lord?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:36.06,0:14:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You're alive!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:37.85,0:14:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, please tell me what to do!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:40.61,0:14:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:42.26,0:14:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, come back!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:44.98,0:14:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You know everything, don't you?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:47.58,0:14:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, I'll do anything!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:49.90,0:14:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as I can fix this,
Dialogue: 5,0:14:52.86,0:14:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter what happens to me!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:40.42,0:15:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The River of Light...
Dialogue: 5,0:15:56.86,0:15:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Mountain Lord!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:59.72,0:16:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Please wait!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:09.78,0:16:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no...
Dialogue: 5,0:16:40.92,0:16:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I...
Dialogue: 5,0:16:44.10,0:16:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}enter that place,
Dialogue: 5,0:16:45.88,0:16:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}then I probably won't be able to come back.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:51.87,0:16:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But that doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:57.31,0:17:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I mean, it's not like I belong anywhere anyway.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:11.36,0:17:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Tokoyami is struggling.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:15.67,0:17:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:17.46,0:17:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you always get in my way?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:32.74,0:17:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I see.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:38.14,0:17:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You just want to live.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:53.12,0:18:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Did it just tell me to go back?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:01.94,0:19:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Do I... even deserve to go back?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:10.43,0:19:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\alpha&H40&}Hey!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:13.40,0:19:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\alpha&H40&}Ginko!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:27.12,0:19:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Ginko!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:28.08,0:19:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You're{ alive}...
Dialogue: 5,0:19:29.77,0:19:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:33.11,0:19:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:37.49,0:19:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:54.61,0:19:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:57.33,0:20:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,These mountains will have to shut down \Nfor the time being, then.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:03.83,0:20:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Is the natural order gone forever?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:08.37,0:20:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going to happen to these mountains?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:13.94,0:20:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What you saw back there was the natural order itself.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:18.21,0:20:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,If you think of the mountain lords as flowers blooming on the surface, what you saw are their roots.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:25.39,0:20:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Since they accepted the mountain lord's life,
Dialogue: 5,0:20:29.02,0:20:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm certain another will appear again someday.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:34.92,0:20:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then, you should get ready to leave.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:39.06,0:20:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't forgive you for what you've done.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:43.56,0:20:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope I never see you again.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:07.48,0:21:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Might as well call it a day here.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:19.25,0:21:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope I never see you again.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:24.85,0:21:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,However, you shouldn't forget:
Dialogue: 5,0:21:29.40,0:21:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,there is no place in this world where we don't belong.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:35.71,0:21:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That includes you.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:37.79,0:21:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The natural order let you come back.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:43.94,0:21:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter where you go, you'll always belong there.
